## Task 2 The Desktop (GUI)

- Login Screen: requires valid credentials (local account or Active Directory).
Desktop Components:
- Desktop: shortcuts to files, folders, programs. Customizable via right-click (arrangement, resolution, wallpaper, themes).
- Start Menu: access to apps, files, utilities.
- Left section: account actions, settings, power options.
- Middle section: recently added and installed apps (alphabetical list).
- Right section: tiles for pinned apps/programs.
- Taskbar: shows running apps/programs, supports pinning, previews, and toolbars.
- Notification Area: bottom-right corner with date/time, volume, network icons. Configurable via Taskbar settings.

